        <mxCell id="lXYNOYBoG4hww80YQewd-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. Client should be able to register and login&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;2. Client should be able to search for an item&lt;br&gt;3. Client should be able to see the details of the product&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Client should be able to add the product to the cart and order it&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Client should be able to check the ststus of the order.&lt;br&gt;5. Client should be able to do the payment&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
